{"tid":2430740,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［正視聽］我地連登認證 葉劉係真黃絲！！","createTime":"2021-03-03T06:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T07:33:32.000Z","uid":14090,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"af6a2c9a49adffcd6b04a2339c3c7f472bd48918","tid":2430740,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"田：葉太用「文革式批鬥」令部分深藍不滿<br />\n<br />\n田北辰表示，葉劉淑儀為劉利群發聲時，用了「文革式批鬥」一詞，或令部分深藍人士不滿，因此可見社交網上有很多網民留言辱罵葉太，指控她「護短」、「暗黃」，甚至「想收買人心」等等，多難聽都有。他指從海量的咒罵聲中，也有部分人提出實質理據，指劉利群當時在食環署的工作，對「止暴制亂」的工作有不利影響。<br />\n<br />\n啱先睇到連登有個post <br />\n入面有篇報導聲稱好多藍營話佢暗黃（乜乜01就唔撚貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n錯哂啦你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">葉劉係真黃絲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n證據如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFBaPqn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFBaPqn.png&h=15a7f6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">葉劉食黃店 支持黃色經濟圈</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dqCuqD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dqCuqD.jpg&h=a951b9ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\">葉劉著黃衫 仲話感謝每一位市民</span>（我諗佢想感謝200萬市民）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">葉劉係真黃絲 咪再話佢暗黃/藍</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">保護手足 你我有責</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c2c74ddd6bb585e6d22eb09e49a521c49d58af","tid":2430740,"uid":14090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"姐姐係真黃絲 你班藍營既咪再老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地連登絕對支持手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d1bb37aa33050582405f2e0c4cd88a95dfdc04","tid":2430740,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"葉太係曹營咁多年原來個心都仲係漢室度"},{"pid":"9cd63adc7abbce81a59962bad8eb5f76744d641f","tid":2430740,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:55:18.000Z","msg":"田北辰籲愛國陣營勿再「互片」　嘆有人「爭住表現自己」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2430321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2430321</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d6162af6c9932d80ce5b9cfcccb5a3a920d28cd","tid":2430740,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2d1bb37aa33050582405f2e0c4cd88a95dfdc04","tid":2430740,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:54:57.000Z","msg":"葉太係曹營咁多年原來個心都仲係漢室度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"好感動 我覺得葉劉真係稱得上真黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc562c5564d644756ba9d014a2826550f4e133c0","tid":2430740,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"佢係英國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb047569a7e2620f4573e9e443c96a654c2faf8c","tid":2430740,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"葉太真黃絲 推到藍營驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c22f63fb265518a7edf6094f94008b5455b8f3","tid":2430740,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bc562c5564d644756ba9d014a2826550f4e133c0","tid":2430740,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"佢係英國製造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:57:32.000Z","msg":"係喎 仲要係港英政府下出產既精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fa35954e25af538fdf9ad23fb403c12e9eec42","tid":2430740,"uid":340729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl